\c 10
\s UThola loJayiri
\p
\v 1 Emva kukaAbhimeleki kwasekuvela uThola indodana kaPhuwa indodana kaDodo, indoda yakoIsakari ukukhulula uIsrayeli; wayehlala eShamiri entabeni yakoEfrayimi\x + Josh. 24.33.\x*.
\v 2 Wasesahlulela uIsrayeli iminyaka engamatshumi amabili lantathu. Wafa, wangcwatshelwa eShamiri.
\p
\v 3 Lemva kwakhe kwavela uJayiri umGileyadi, wahlulela uIsrayeli iminyaka engamatshumi amabili lambili.
\v 4 Wayelamadodana angamatshumi amathathu agada amathole abobabhemi\x + 5.10.\x* angamatshumi amathathu, elemizi engamatshumi amathathu, abayithi yiHavothi-Jayiri kuze kube lamuhla\x + Dute. 3.14.\x*, eselizweni leGileyadi.
\v 5 UJayiri wasesifa, wangcwatshelwa eKamoni.
\p
\v 6 Abantwana bakoIsrayeli basebebuya besenza okubi emehlweni eN\nd kosi\x + 2.11; 3.7; 4.1; 6.1; 13.1.\x*\nd*, bakhonza oBhali \w laboAshitarothi\w**\x + 2.13.\x*, labonkulunkulu beSiriya labonkulunkulu beSidoni\x + 1 Kho. 11.5,7,33. 2 Kho. 23.13.\x* labonkulunkulu bakoMowabi labonkulunkulu babantwana bakoAmoni labonkulunkulu bamaFilisti\x + 16.23.\x*; bayitshiya iN\nd kosi\x + 10.10,13. Dute. 31.16.\x*\nd*, kabaze bayikhonza.
\v 7 Ulaka lweN\nd kosi\nd* lwaselumvuthela uIsrayeli, yabathengisa ezandleni zamaFilisti\x + Dute. 32.30.\x* lezandleni zabantwana bakoAmoni\x + 1 Sam. 11.1.\x*.
\v 8 Asebachitha abacindezela abantwana bakoIsrayeli\x + Eks. 15.6.\x* ngalowomnyaka\x + 10.5.\x* - iminyaka elitshumi leyisificaminwembili, bonke abantwana bakoIsrayeli ababengaphetsheya kweJordani elizweni lamaAmori eliseGileyadi.
\v 9 Njalo abantwana bakoAmoni bachapha iJordani ukuze balwe ngitsho bemelene loJuda\x + 1 Sam. 11.1.\x* njalo bemelene loBhenjamini bemelene lendlu kaEfrayimi; ngalokho uIsrayeli wacindezeleka\x + 2.15.\x* kakhulu.
\p
\v 10 Abantwana bakoIsrayeli basebekhala eN\nd kosi\nd*ni\x + 3.9.\x* besithi: Sonile kuwe, njalo ngoba sitshiyile uNkulunkulu wethu\x + 10.10,13. Dute. 31.16.\x*, sasesikhonza oBhali.
\v 11 IN\nd kosi\nd* yasisithi ebantwaneni bakoIsrayeli: Kangi\add likhulula\add*nga yini kumaGibhithe\x + Eks. 14.30.\x* lakumaAmori\x + Nani 21.21,22,23,24,33,34,35.\x* lakubantwana bakoAmoni\x + 3.13.\x* lakumaFilisti\x + 3.13.\x*?
\v 12 AmaSidoni lawo lamaAmaleki\x + 3.13; 5.14; 6.3.\x* lamaMahoni\x + 2 Lan. 26.7. 1 Lan. 4.41.\x* alicindezela\x + Hlab. 106.42,43.\x*, laselikhala kimi, ngalikhulula esandleni sawo.
\v 13 Kanti lina lingitshiyile\x + 10.6. Dute. 32.15. Jer. 2.13.\x* lakhonza abanye onkulunkulu; ngakho kangisayikulikhulula.
\v 14 Hambani liyekhala kubonkulunkulu elibakhethileyo\x + Dute. 32.37,38.\x*; kabalikhulule bona ngesikhathi sokuhlupheka kwenu.
\p
\v 15 Abantwana bakoIsrayeli-ke bathi eN\nd kosi\nd*ni: Sonile; yenza wena kithi njengakho konke okuhle emehlweni akho; kuphela sikhulule, siyakuncenga, lamuhla.
\v 16 Basebesusa onkulunkulu bezizweni phakathi kwabo, bakhonza iN\nd kosi\nd*; umphefumulo wayo\x + 2.18.\x* wasudabuka ngohlupho lukaIsrayeli\x + Isa. 63.9.\x*.
\v 17 Kwasekubizelwa ndawonye abantwana bakoAmoni, bamisa inkamba eGileyadi, labantwana bakoIsrayeli babuthana bamisa inkamba eMizipa\x + 11.11,29. Josh. 11.3.\x*.
\v 18 Labantu, iziphathamandla zeGileyadi, bathi omunye komunye: Ngubani umuntu ozaqala ukulwa emelene labantwana bakoAmoni? Uzakuba yinhloko phezu kwabo bonke abahlali beGileyadi\x + 11.5,6,8,11.\x*.